<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Acreage and lifestyle in the Redlands hinterland.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Mount Cotton is one of south-east Brisbane's most distinctive lifestyle suburbs, a band of acreage and rural-residential blocks sitting between Capalaba and Redland Bay. Cleared hobby blocks, larger family acreage and bushland-backed lifestyle properties give the suburb a clear identity that buyers travel a long way to find.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
