        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Targeted acreage buyer pool</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/sheldon" style="color:#c4912a;">Sheldon</a>, <a href="/suburbs/capalaba" style="color:#c4912a;">Capalaba</a>, <a href="/suburbs/burbank" style="color:#c4912a;">Burbank</a>.</p>
